            "title": "恒生指數公司推出恒生高息股30指數",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　《經濟通通訊社14日專訊》恒生指數公司宣布今天推出恒生高息股30指數(HSHD30),旨在反映基於恒生大中型股(可投資)指數內的30隻高股息率證券。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">(cl)</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\"></p></section></main>",
            "link": "https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/5900920",
