            "title": "盤中速報 - IET-KY(4971)大跌7.09%，報124.5元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>IET-KY(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4971:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4971\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4971-TW</a>)14日12:49股價下跌9.5元，報124.5元，跌幅7.09%，成交11,455張。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>IET-KY(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4971:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4971\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4971-TW</a>)所屬產業為半導體業，主要業務為GaAs pHEMT epi wafers。InP HBT epi wafers。GaSb infrared material and epi wafers。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>近5日股價下跌18.79%，櫃買市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>下跌4.23%，短期股價無明顯表現。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：+613 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：+270 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：0 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：+343 張</li> <li>融資增減：-306 張</li> <li>融券增減：-443 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
